[{"id":"a76ad1b275b15cec1c7c755d9706bae8","from":"Erik Wachtmeister","from_email":"erikw@bestofallworlds.com","to":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to_list":[{"name":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"Oversubscribed Equity Crowd-Funding","date":"2014-04-30T19:04:15.000Z","formatted_date":"Apr 30, 2014","formatted_time":"7:04 PM","body":"Email not displaying correctly? View it ( http://sendgrid.org/wf/webmail?rp=ZTI1bGQzTnNaWFIwWlhKZmFXUTZNVEl6TkN4MWMyVnlYMmxrT2pJMU5qVTBmUWV5SnVaWGR6YkdWMGRHVnlYMmxrSWpvaU1qWTNNRGN4TXlJc0ltNWxkM05zWlhSMFpYSmZkWE5sY2w5cFpDSTZORFkwTWpFM01USTFOVEY5 ) in your browser\n\nDear\u00a0Jeffrey,\n\n\n\u00a0\n\nWith a week to go on Crowdcube in the UK and in Sweden, Best of All Worlds has received formal commitments for over the full amount, and we are now oversubscribed. (bit.ly/boawoffer ( http://bit.ly/boawoffer ))\n\n\nWe have decided that we will continue taking on additional investors for the time being.\u00a0For those interested in participating, we would recommend acting in the next few days, with the offering closing on May 5th.\u00a0\n\n\nFor those in the US, we are also live on SeedInvest, where US-based accredited investors can participate directly via a Delaware C Corp. (bit.ly/boawseed ( http://bit.ly/boawseed )).\n\n\nCrowd-funding has proven to be a great way for some of our members to become stakeholders and be part of the development of Best of All Worlds\n\n\u00a0\n\n\nWarm regards,\nErik\n\n\n\u00a0\n\nBest of All Worlds\n\nBest of All Worlds\u2019 mission is to be the leading global social network and discovery platform, where members can interact around their social and professional interests, in a trusted and relevant Friends of Friends environment.\n\nThis message was sent to\u00a0jeeproject@yahoo.com\u00a0because email notifications are enabled for this account.\n\u00a0\n\nTo change your email preferences, go to\u00a0account settings ( https://www.bestofallworlds.com/account/settings ).